programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.desc: While attempting to steal land from an Indian tribe, crooked ranchers kill one of the braves. The Judge must move fast to prevent an all-out massacre. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel, and Jackie Laughery.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.desc: Waiting to hear whether or not gold has been struck in the mine, Annie discovers a beloved stagecoach is being driven by the daughter of the owner, whos threatening to sell the stage so he can pocket the money. When word comes back that there is no gold in the money, Annie becomes suspicious and begins investigating. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.sub-title: S01 : E06 Annie Calls Her Shots
programme.desc: After a jailed Dobie escapes from jail, Dobie and Tagg find themselves kidnapped, forcing a desperate Annie to rescue her brother. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This entertaining western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: George Washington helps a young woman whose land is being threatened by an innkeeper. Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper .Episode originally aired in 1957.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: A group of wives living on the frontier aim to join their husbands for the holidays.Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by Jams Fenimore Cooper. Episode originally aired in 1957.

programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: After Farmer Perkins murders a store clerk in front of his wife, and is allowed to walk after his trial, the Cartwrights step in to make sure hell be rearrested, tried, and hung.Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.title: Leather Burners
programme.desc: Hopalong Cassidy (William Boyd) gets the call when a herd of rustled cattle mysteriously disappear. Andy Clyde, Victor Jory and George Reeves (televisions Superman!) also star in this, the 42nd of 66 Hopalong Cassidy features. If you look closely, you might even notice Robert Mitchum in an uncredited role!

programme.title: New Mexico
programme.desc: What happens when Abraham Lincoln himself comes to New Mexico to discuss a treaty with Native American chief Acoma (Ted de Corsia)? Can the hotbed of emotions be quieted by cavalry Captain Hunt (Lew Ayres)? Or will the Captains superiors insist on provoking with the native tribe? Find out what happens in this fictional tale packed with action from 1951!

programme.title: Colorado
programme.desc: Theres trouble out west! Its the Civil War and the Union needs troops back east to defend itself. Roy Rogers stars as Lieutenant Jerry Burke, who is sent to investigate why the returning troops are being stalled in Colorado. Also starring Gabby Hayes, Pauline Moore, and Milburn Stone, this film is action packed with a turn you wont see coming!

programme.title: Six Gun Trail
programme.desc: Legendary cowboy star Tim McCoy stars as Captain William Carson, who along with his sidekick Magpie does battle with jewel thieves. Its an actionfilled drama of the West, with plenty of blazing guns and heman adventure! There are a couple of songs, too, including Moon Over the Plains but they arent sung by Tim McCoy. He was too darned tough to sing! Also starring Nora Lane, Ben Corbet; directed by Sam Newfield.

programme.title: Hurricane Horseman
programme.desc: Pancho Gomez kidnaps Don Roberto and his daughter, Tonita for ransom. Can an undercover lawman named Gun Smith save the pair, or will he be caught himself?! Smith gets a job in Gomezs camp supposedly to repair their guns. Instead he fixes the guns so they will misfire. When Gomez refuses to let him go, he sends his horse for the Sheriff! This campy western from 1931 stars Lane Chandler and is sure to keep you enthralled from beginning to end. Directed by Armand Schaefer; starring Marie Quillan and Walter Miller.

programme.title: Randy Rides Alone
programme.desc: John Wayne was 27 when he starred in this vintage western drama from Hollywoods Poverty Row. He plays Randy Bowers, a man wrongly jailed for murders. With help from a female friend, he breaks out of prison and sets out to find the real killers. Harry L. Fraser (The Last of the Clintons, Rustlers Paradise) directs a strong cast of familiar faces, including legendary sidekick George Gabby Hayes, Earl Dwyer, and one of the hardest ridin stuntmen turned actors, Yakima Canutt.

programme.title: High Lonesome
programme.desc: A young drifter is suspected of murder in this stirring production from writer/director Alan Le May (best known for writing The Searchers). John Drew Barrymore stars as Cooncat, a troubled young man who has to steal to survive. With no friends in West Texas, he falls in with some bad customers who involve him in some terrible crimes. The strong cast includes Chill Wills, Jack Elam, and John Archer, with cinematography by Oscar winner W. Howard Greene.

programme.title: Painted Desert
programme.desc: A mightly melodrama of red-blooded action, William Boyd stars in the Pre-Code western talkie - The Painted Desert (1931). The first sound film for Hollywood heavyweight Clark Gable, The Painted Desert finds Boyd and Gable at odds over the affections of a cowboys beautiful daughter (Helen Twelvetrees).

programme.title: Colorado Kid
programme.desc: Cowboy star Bob Steele (Valley of Hunted Men, The Trail Blazers) headlines this Poverty Row western drama. As the Colorado Kid, hes falsely arrested for murder and has to clear himself. The colorful cast includes Ernie Adams, Frank LaRue, and Horace Murphy, with direction by Sam Newfield (The Terror of Tiny Town, The Mad Monster).

programme.title: The Gunman from Bodie
programme.desc: The Rough Riders, a popular group that thrilled audiences in the early 1940s, are after a gang of rustlers in this B-western from Hollywoods Poverty Row. Starring Buck Jones, Tim McCoy, and Raymond Hatton, this movie features everything from lawmen going undercover to the Rough Riders looking after an orphaned baby! Also, be on the lookout for the beautiful Christine McIntyre, who would go on to appear in several of the Three Stooges shorts for Colombia Pictures.

programme.title: Brand of the Devil
programme.desc: The Texas Rangers tangle with a band of dangerous rustlers in this two-fisted production from Hollywoods Poverty Row. Starring Dave OBrien, Kermit Maynard, and Guy Wilkerson, with direction by low-budget ace Harry L. Fraser.

programme.title: Bulldog Courage
programme.desc: Tim McCoy, one of the unsung heroes of 1930s western pictures, stars in a dual role. First, hes Slim Braddock, a miner who turns to robbing stagecoaches after being swindled by a banker. When Slim is murdered, his son Tim, also played by McCoy, seeks vengeance. Directed by B-movie legend Sam Newfield for Excelsior Pictures, this film is a showcase for McCoy, who appeared in more than 90 movies and in 1960 earned a star on the Hollywood Walk of Fame!

programme.title: With Sitting Bull at the Spirit Lake Massacre
programme.desc: A long-thought-lost film finally surfaces after being unseen for over eight decades. Created and copyrighted by Sunset Productions in 1925 but not released until June 15, 1927, this silent epic features the superior Native American actor Chief Yowlachie (performing here under the name Chief Yowlache) as Sitting Bull. Other fine actors in the cast include the always popular Bryant Washburn and a young Bob Steele, who appears under his real name Bob Bradbury Jr. The story takes place in the 1860s or 1870s near Spirit Lake, Iowa. Settlements of whites are growing in that region but the Sioux Indians also have professed their interest in one such settlement. Chief Sitting Bull surveys the...

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: Pat and Stoney take time out from their duties to try and collect the bounty posted on a legendary golden wolf that roams the Colorado foothills. A couple of wolf hunters dont take kindly to a pair of amateur hunters horning in on their range and attempt to drive the G-Men away before they can capture or kill their quarry.

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: Pat and Stoney travel to Wyoming to oversee a land opening and end up playing nursemaid to a pair of identical twin pranksters and a kooky Chinese cook. Meanwhile, a trio of outlaws are pursuing the twins seeking information they possess. Starring Russell Hayden, Jackie Coogan.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.desc: When Herby (Don Washbrook) gets drafted, Kate tries to cheer him up by saying he could become an astronaut. Could hooterville actually send someone ito the space program? Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Series created by Paul Henning. Episode first aired in 1963.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.sub-title: S01 : E16 Bobbie Jo and the Beatnik
programme.desc: Bobbie Jo falls head over heals for an edgy young poet from New York. He likes her, too, but hes not fond of Hooterville. Of coure, Kate has to show Bobby Jo what this pompous fool is all about. Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Series created by Paul Henning. Episode first aired in 1963. Look for Dennis Hopper as the beatnik.

programme.title: Cisco Kid
programme.desc: Cisco and Pancho work to uncover a cattle rustling operation.Starring Duncan Renaldo as The Cisco Kid, and Leo Carillo as Pancho. This weekly adventure series was a favorite of the 1950s, following two pals as they traveled the old west, righting wrongs and helping the underdog..The show was nominated for a PrimeTime Emmy Award in 1951. This episode aired in 1950. The show was produced by ZIV Television, the same company that gave us Highway Patrol and Sea Hunt.

programme.title: Cisco Kid
programme.desc: Cisco and Pancho investigate when a railway detective is found dead.Starring Duncan Renaldo as The Cisco Kid, and Leo Carillo as Pancho. This weekly adventure series was a favorite of the 1950s, following two pals as they traveled the old west, righting wrongs and helping the underdog. The show was produced by ZIV Television, the same company that gave us Highway Patrol and Sea Hunt, and was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1951 This episode first aired in 1950.

programme.title: Stories of the Century
programme.desc: Detective Matt Clark goes undercover working at a gambling den. Starring Jim Davis and Mary Castle. Directed by William Witney. Produced by B movie veteran Edward J. White. Episode first aired in 1954.Series won an Emmy in 1955. Also starring Dick SImmons, Claire Carleton, Mauritz Hugo, Howard Wright, and Douglas Evans.

programme.title: Stories of the Century
programme.desc: Detective Frankie is shot during a robbery. Her life becomes in danger when her doctor is kidnapped by the murderous outlaw Clay Allison.Starring Jim Davis, Mary Castle, Jack Kelly, Paul Farber, Frank Fenton, and Fred Sherman.Directed by William Witney. Episode first aired in 1954. Produced by B movie veteran Edward White. Series won an Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.desc: In Family Ties, Judge Bean comes to the aid of the Peralta family as unscrupulous real estate agents try to force them off their land. Theyve learned that a railroad will need the property and they intend to make an undeserved profit. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel.

programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.desc: In this episode, crooks posing as newspapermen attempt to blackmail a local rancher in order to steal his land and property. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel, and Jackie Laughery.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.sub-title: S01 : E11 Valley of the Shadows
programme.desc: Annie tries to help a blind girl find her fathers killer. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. Directed by Robert G. Walker. Also starring Judy Nugent, Forrest Taylor, and Denver Pyle. This entertaining western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy Award in 1955.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.sub-title: S01 : E12 Annie and the Lily Maid
programme.desc: Choctaw looks to inherit the ranch of the murdered Sam Forbes, but Elaine, a previously unknown niece, appears, making Annie suspicious as the men fall for her seemingly delicate nature. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: Tensions rise between the settlers and the Ottawas. Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper. Episode originally aired in 1957.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: Hawkeye becomes embroiled in a fortune hunters search for treasure. Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild.Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper. Episode originally aired in 1957.

programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: After the Virginia City bank is robbed by an outlaw gang, the gangs youngest member gets a job on the Ponderosa. Initially welcomed, Little Joe becomes suspicious of Ponderosas newest member.Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.title: Prairie Pals
programme.desc: ITS A MODERN GOLD RUSH GANGSTER STYLE! But Three Ridin Singin Fightin Buckaroos Stop Em Cold! The Prairie Pals are on the lookout for Wainwright, a scientist who has gone missing after discovering a way to turn vanadium ore into gold. The Prairie Pals start their search at Hank Stoners land, where the vanadium ore can be found. Directed by Sam Newfield; starring Bill Cowboy Rambler Boyd, Art Davis, and Lee Powell.

programme.title: Cowboy and the Senorita
programme.desc: Roy Rogers and Trigger get top billing in this one, while the senorita of the title, Dale Evans, is billed fourth. Maybe Dale needed a better agent! Then again, who pays attention to screen credits when you have such a funfilled fiesta of thrills and action? Roys most zestful musical adventure is about a worthless gold mine that turns out to have a hidden shaft filled with riches. But can Roy make the claim while hes trying to outrun a trumped up robbery charge? Its romance, rhythm, and revelry, all from Republic Pictures. Musical numbers include Bunk House Bugle Boy and Besame Mucho, plus the beautiful title song performed by Roy!

programme.title: Heart of the Golden West
programme.desc: Roy Rogers, Gabby Hayes, and Smiley Burnette team up to protect the ranchers of Cherokee City from the false charges of illegal cattle trafficking. It may seem like the odds are against Roy, but just watch as he changes the course of the law with his flaming bullets, and, of course, a few songs. For trivia buffs: Smiley Burnette joined Roy because Gene Autry, the actor for whom he usually served as a sidekick, had joined the service!

programme.title: Tumbleweeds
programme.desc: The great William S. Hart stars in this classic tale of settlers in the Oklahoma territory. Directed by King Baggot, one of the most versatile movie figures of the silent era, this movie is not only history recorded in heart throbs, as the original print ads boasted, but shows us why Hart is considered by some to be the top western actor of them all. Hart, who directed many of his own films, also had a hand in directing this feature, which turned out to be his last starring role.

programme.title: Rawhide
programme.desc: Baseball superstar Gehrig is one of several ranchers being coerced by a bunch of bandits. His sister and her lawyer/lover organize the ranchers. Directed by Ray Taylor; starring Smith Ballew, Gehrig, Evelyn Knapp. Talk about stunt casting! Gehrig was a New York Yankees star who was nearing the end of his career, but one of the biggest sports stars in the country. In the movie he plays a variation of himself, as Lou Gehrig, a retired baseball player who takes up ranching. Lou expects to relax on his ranch but quickly joins other ranchers in a fight to protect their properties.

programme.title: The Lucky Texan
programme.desc: John Wayne stars in this vintage western. He and George Gabby Hayes strike it rich with a gold mine, only to find their lives complicated by women and crooked officials. Things get even messier when the good guys are framed for murder! Its all action here, particularly since legendary stuntman Yakima Cannut stars as one of the films heavies. Who will win the fight over the gold and the girl? Directed by Robert N. Bradbury for Monogram Pictures. Also starring Barbara Sheldon. (The film was also known as Gold Strike River.)

programme.title: The Sundowners
programme.desc: Brother battles brother in this gritty tale of feuding ranchers in the old west. This story of the Texas panhandle stars such familiar faces as Robert Preston, Chill Wills, and Jack Elam, and was a rare film for its time in that it was filmed almost entirely in Texas with no studio interiors. If for no other reason, watch this one for Prestons performance. If you only know him from The Music Man or Victor Victoria, youre sure to be surprised here! (also, look for John Drew Barrymore as Jef Cloud. He was part of the famous Barrymore family, and father of Drew Barrymore.) Jim Strake: Frank Cordell. The Whip: Dave Kashner. Directed by George Templeton

programme.title: The Outlaw
programme.desc: Billy the Kid, Pat Garrett, and Doc Holliday ride again in Howard Hughes epic 1943 western, but the character youll remember most is sultry country vixen Rio McDonald. Hughes nationwide search for an actress to play Rio resulted in the film debut of Jane Russell, whose natural assets were allegedly helped by a special bra designed by Hughes. When The Outlaw finally received a nationwide release in 1946, its success vindicated Hughes and made Russell a star. As for Hughes infamous bra, Russell said in her 1988 memoir, I never wore it, and he never knew.

programme.title: Hamlet i affarsvarlden
programme.desc: Efter sin faders dod arver Hamlet en styrelseplats i ett gummiforetag. Hamlets farbror kontrollerar foretaget och bestammer sig for att de ska satsa på en ny marknad, namligen gummiankor. Men den nyblivne styrelsemedlemmen ar misstanksam, framforallt over omstandigheterna kring faderns dod. Aki Kaurismaki regisserar har en smått bisarr ”film-noir” variant av Shakespeares HAMLET. Aki Kaurismaki ar kand for sina socialrealistiska skildringar och svarta karleksforklaringar till ett dystert Finland. Filmer med komiska och omsinta inslag.

programme.title: Ariel
programme.desc: Taisto jobbar i en gruva i norra Finland. Nar gruvan stangs reser han mot Helsingfors i en vrakig cabriolet som han ovantat får. Men problemen tornar upp sig. Han blir rånad, hittar inget jobb och doms till fangelse for misshandel. Men med hjalp av sin flickvan Irmeli, en ensamstående mor han traffar i Helsingfors och sin cellkamrat planerar Taisto att bryta sig ur fangelset och starta om på nytt. Aki Kaurismaki ar kand for sina socialrealistiska skildringar och svarta karleksforklaringar till ett dystert Finland. Filmer med komiska och omsinta inslag.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: A Polar Year
programme.desc: 28-årige Anders bestammer sig for att resa till Gronland for att undervisa i en liten by. Hans foraldrar tar avstånd från beslutet eftersom de forvantar sig att han ska ta over familjegården, men Anders ser garna ett miljoombyte och nya utmaningar. Livet ar tufft i den lilla byn – tuffare an Anders hade forestallt sig. Byborna tar till en borjan inte emot honom val och om han ska gora sig några forhoppningar om att hjalpa familjerna – inte minst barnen – måste Anders ta ett viktigt beslut. Han måste lara kanna byns manniskor och inte minst deras traditioner. Forst nar han gjort det kommer en helt ny varld att oppna sig for Anders...

programme.title: Cha Cha Cha
programme.desc: Den alkoholiserade Matti (Matti Pellonpaa), som bor under broarna, ar på vag att arva en betydande summa pengar från sin amerikanska faster. Men mannen måste vara representativ under fasterns besok. Matti berattar om situationen for sin van som arbetar som bilhandlare, och denne foreslår en rollbyten mot ersattning.

programme.title: Brott och straff
programme.desc: En filmatisering av Dostojevskijs roman med samma namn, som utspelar sig i 1980-talets Finland. Romanen Brott och straff ar ansedd som en av vår tids storsta litterara verk. Fjodor Dostojevskij målar upp det moraliska dilemmat huruvida ett brott, i det har fallet ett mord ar forsvarbart om resultatet blir positivt for många, om andamålet helgar medlen. Aki Kaurismaki ar kand for sina socialrealistiska och svarta karleksforklaringar till ett dystert Finland med komiska och omsinta inslag.

programme.title: Ettor and Nollor - Part 1
programme.desc: FBI och Interpol får nys om en stor kreditkortsharva och pundaren Sebbe plockas in som misstankt. Nar polisen borjar sina forhor får de hora en otrolig historia från Goteborgs undre varld. Svenska och ryska gangsters, marockanska hackers, korrupta politiker och giriga kostymnissar - alla vill tjana stora pengen, ingen vill vara hunden...

programme.title: Rosso
programme.desc: Rosso, som skickligt kombinerar roadmovie och kriminaldrama, ar berattelsen om den sicilianska lonnmordaren Giancarlo Rosso, som har kommit till Finland for att leta efter sitt nasta mål, som råkar vara hans alskade Marja. Ovantat får Rosso hjalp med spårningen av Marjas bror Martti, trots att de inte ens delar ett gemensamt språk. På resan ingår både skrotningsuppdrag och några rån...

programme.title: Bitchkram
programme.desc: Kristin raknar dagarna till studenten då hon antligen får lamna småstaden och sin manipulativa syster for sina drommars New York. Allt ar perfekt och lokaltidningen på orten har lovat att publicera Kristins kronikor om staden som aldrig sover. Men Kristin missar planet och gommer sig istallet hemma hos Andrea, en marklig ung tjej, långt ute på landet for att undvika total fornedring. I huset ingenstans tar Kristin med Andrea till New Yorks pulserande hjarta i ett vindlande virtuellt aventyr som alla darhemma kan folja i hennes artiklar. Men så tranger sig verkligheten på.

programme.title: Moln på drift
programme.desc: Ilona och Lauri ar ett stravsamt par som inte begar mycket av livet. Tak over huvudet, mat på bordet, ett glas vin och en kvall framfor tv-n. De arbetar plikttroget och agnar sina korta ledigheter åt varandra och sin hund. Men en dag hander något som hotar att slå deras trygga tillvaro i spillror. En varm och absurd historia om ett alldeles vanligt par någonstans i Finland.

programme.title: De arvlosa
programme.desc: Mika Kaurismaens forsta långfilm. Han skrev manuset tillsammans med sin bror Aki. "De arvlosa" ar en tidlos skildring av hur småskurken Manne, bonddrangen Harri och den vackra Veera kor en Volga genom de forsvinnande finlandska landskapen, med poliser och gangsters standigt på halarna. Den fartfyllda resan ackompanjeras av tidlosa låtar av bland annat Juice och Rauli Badding.

programme.title: Så olika
programme.desc: Så olika ar en komedi om karlek. Det kretsar kring två systrar, den ena nytillsatt finansborgarråd i Stockholm, nyskild och mamma till två dottrar. Den andra en sjalvstandig TV-producent som har fått i uppdrag att gora ett nytt direktsant sångprogram från Skansen - nu mitt bland djuren! Den handlar om att bli sanslost foralskad i sin varsta fiende, om manniskor som mots trots att de ar fundamentalt olika. For har overvinner karleken allt - från politisk maktkamp till dans med salarna på Skansen.

programme.title: 30:e november
programme.desc: Adam och hans polare spenderar sin tid med att trakassera invandrare som de hatar. Men så moter Adam Julia från Peru och de blir blixtforalskad, eftersom varken Adams vanner eller Julias familj skulle acceptera att de två ar tillsammans tvingas de hålla sin karlek hemlig. På Sveriges nationaldag drabbas Adam och hans gang samman med Julias bror, Sascha, och hans vanner. Det hela slutar med att två dodads.

programme.title: Lindell - Sorgmanteln - Del 1
programme.desc: Fyra små flickor på ett fotografi. Tjugo år senare hittas en av dem mordad. En annan ar spårlost forsvunnen. Cato Isaksen ar redo att losa nya kriminalgåtor. Lise Sommer blir upphunnen av sitt forflutna. Hennes basta van Esther Synnøve Lønn har hittats mordad med avskuren hals. Några dagar senare forsvinner Esthers son. Nar polisen borjar att skrapa på ytan visar det sig att en barndomsvan till Lise och Esther Synnøve också saknas. Forhållandet mellan vaninnorna doljer morka understrommar. Vad var det egentligen som hande nar flickorna var små? Och deras mammor - vad doljer de?

programme.title: Lindell: Dromfångaren - Del 1
programme.desc: En olidligt spannande kriminalhistoria dar de psykologiska undertonerna bar handlingen framåt tills det hela slutar i en dramatisk kapplopning med en iskall mordare. Vem ar fonstertittaren som som står och betraktar de unga kvinnorna i lagenheten mitt emot? Har han något med mordet på nittonåriga Therese Geber att gora? Är det samma man som tar sig in i deras lagenhet på natterna? Kriminalkommissarie Cato Isaksen får ett nytt fall på halsen.

programme.title: De dodas tjarn
programme.desc: Inspirerad av boken ”De dodas tjarn” av Bernhard Borge. Lillians tvillingbror Bjorn dor på ett mystiskt satt ensam vid den gamla familjestugan. Nu, ett år senare, kommer Lillian med sina vanner till stugan for att ta farval och salja stallet. Strax efter ankomsten borjar underliga saker att handa. Lillian går i somnen och kan inte skilja mardrom från verklighet. Någon eller några jagar dem och till slut dyker ett lik upp. Är legenden om Tore Gruvik på vag att bli verklighet eller ar fienden en av dem? Vad skedde forra sommaren och vad var fel på Bjorn Werner?

programme.title: Going To Kansas City
programme.desc: Kansas City, here we come” ropar Mikko (Mikko Nousiainen) nar han åker till Kansas City i USA som utbytesstudent. I stallet for storstad hamnar han andå till en småstad som heter Canaan, och dar ar frammande inte alltid valkomna. Mikko faller for vacker Carly Malone, dotter till stans forbittrad assisterande sheriff (Michael Ironside).

programme.title: Odd Man Rush
programme.desc: Odd Man Rush ar baserad på Bill Keenans bastsaljande sjalvbiografi med samma namn. Filmens Bobby Sanders flyttar från Harvards hockeylag till div. 1 i Sverige, i en deal som inbegriper en tvattmaskin och torktumlare. Hans romantisk relation med en tjej i ortens mataffar tvingar honom att se livets realiteter i ogonen och rejalt fundera om barndomsdrommen att spela i NHL ar realistisk.

programme.title: Bitchkram
programme.desc: Kristin raknar dagarna till studenten då hon antligen får lamna småstaden och sin manipulativa syster for sina drommars New York. Allt ar perfekt och lokaltidningen på orten har lovat att publicera Kristins kronikor om staden som aldrig sover. Men Kristin missar planet och gommer sig istallet hemma hos Andrea, en marklig ung tjej, långt ute på landet for att undvika total fornedring. I huset ingenstans tar Kristin med Andrea till New Yorks pulserande hjarta i ett vindlande virtuellt aventyr som alla darhemma kan folja i hennes artiklar. Men så tranger sig verkligheten på.

programme.title: Så olika
programme.desc: Så olika ar en komedi om karlek. Det kretsar kring två systrar, den ena nytillsatt finansborgarråd i Stockholm, nyskild och mamma till två dottrar. Den andra en sjalvstandig TV-producent som har fått i uppdrag att gora ett nytt direktsant sångprogram från Skansen - nu mitt bland djuren! Den handlar om att bli sanslost foralskad i sin varsta fiende, om manniskor som mots trots att de ar fundamentalt olika. For har overvinner karleken allt - från politisk maktkamp till dans med salarna på Skansen.

programme.title: Moln på drift
programme.desc: Ilona och Lauri ar ett stravsamt par som inte begar mycket av livet. Tak over huvudet, mat på bordet, ett glas vin och en kvall framfor tv-n. De arbetar plikttroget och agnar sina korta ledigheter åt varandra och sin hund. Men en dag hander något som hotar att slå deras trygga tillvaro i spillror. En varm och absurd historia om ett alldeles vanligt par någonstans i Finland.

programme.title: Long Story Short
programme.desc: Det har ar berattelsen om Ellen och hennes vanner, och deras mer eller mindre sjalvforvållat komplicerade karleksliv och romantiska drommar. Tre år av vannernas basta och samsta karlekshistorier sammanfattas och berattas genom åtta kapitel, som alla utspelar sig vid olika festliga tillstallningar. Gruppen kampar med iden om det perfekta forhållandet och måste omvardera vad sann karlek egentligen ar.

programme.title: Den Svavelgula Himlen
programme.desc: Forfattaren Frej blev i tonåren kar i overklasstjejen Stella Rabell. Deras starka band overlevde mot alla odds det stormiga forhållandet under decennierna som foljde. Nar Stellas storebror Alex blir knivhuggen borjar Frej tanka tillbaka till saker som har hant från det lyckliga 70-talet och framåt.

programme.title: Mannen utan minne
programme.desc: Aki Kaurismakis film om en man som tappar sitt minne och får hjalp av fattiga men storhjartade manniskor i en containerby.

programme.title: Zombie och spoktåget
programme.desc: Zombie (Silu Seppala: Leningrad Cowboys) ar en individ som går sin egen vag och inte kan folja de normer som det finska samhallet har satt for honom. Zombie beslutar sig for att lamna allt och ge sig utomlands - till en plats dar ingen forvantar sig något av honom. Zombie och spoktåget betraktas av många som några av Mika Kaurismakis basta filmer. Filmen belonades med Jussi-priset for Basta regissor, Basta manliga huvudroll och Basta foto år 1992. Tragikomiskt och aven surrealistiskt foljer Zombie med bland andra Mato Valtonen och Sakke Jarvenpaa från Sleepy Sleepers, samt naturligtvis Matti Pellonpaa.

programme.title: Hotet
programme.desc: Lasse Brudell ar ansvarig programmerare vid flygbasen i Vidsel i Norrbotten. Han arbetar med det topphemliga forsvarssystemet EWS till JAS Gripen. Major Haglund som leder en militar specialstyrka, ar en desillusionerad och arrad krigsveteran. Deras vagar korsas nar Haglund kallas in for att hoja sakerhetsrutinerna infor en demonstration av Gripen for utlandska intressenter. Den eftertraktade mjukvaran ar hårdvaluta i det internationella maktspelet och måste skyddas.

programme.title: Projekt Z
programme.desc: En grupp filmstudenter tar med sig tre lediga skådespelare till ett nedlagt hotell i de norska fjallen for att spela in en zombiefilm. Deras fiktion blir plotsligt verklighet nar en okand varelse borjar terrorisera filminspelningen.

programme.title: Lindell: Dromfångaren - Del 2
programme.desc: En olidligt spannande kriminalhistoria dar de psykologiska undertonerna bar handlingen framåt tills det hela slutar i en dramatisk kapplopning med en iskall mordare. Vem ar fonstertittaren som som står och betraktar de unga kvinnorna i lagenheten mitt emot? Har han något med mordet på nittonåriga Therese Geber att gora? Är det samma man som tar sig in i deras lagenhet på natterna? Kriminalkommissarie Cato Isaksen får ett nytt fall på halsen.

programme.title: Hamlet i affarsvarlden
programme.desc: Efter sin faders dod arver Hamlet en styrelseplats i ett gummiforetag. Hamlets farbror kontrollerar foretaget och bestammer sig for att de ska satsa på en ny marknad, namligen gummiankor. Men den nyblivne styrelsemedlemmen ar misstanksam, framforallt over omstandigheterna kring faderns dod. Aki Kaurismaki regisserar har en smått bisarr ”film-noir” variant av Shakespeares HAMLET. Aki Kaurismaki ar kand for sina socialrealistiska skildringar och svarta karleksforklaringar till ett dystert Finland. Filmer med komiska och omsinta inslag.

programme.title: Skuggor i paradiset
programme.desc: Nikander ar en ensam sopbils-chauffor som en dag moter den anspråkslosa snabbkopskassorskan Ilona. Nikander blir blixtrande kar, men deras omsesidiga blyghet medfor att det romantiska lyser med sin frånvaro. Så plotsligt andras livet… Ilona får sparken och de bestammer sig for att traffas på ett mysigt litet motell. Aki Kaurismaki ar kand for sina socialrealistiska skildringar och svarta karleksforklaringar till ett dystert Finland. Filmer med komiska och omsinta inslag.

programme.title: Just Friends
programme.desc: Får vi presentera Chris Bander. Highschool på nittiotalet var en pina: han var blyg, overviktig och hemligt foralskad i Jamie, hans enda kompis och tillika en av skolans mest populara hejarklacksledare. Men nar han antligen hade lyckats samla mod nog att gora en framstot, ville hon bara att de skulle vara vanner! I dag ar Chris en aslacker skivproducent i LA och kan valja bland en uppsjo av vackra och villiga tjejer. Och nar han plotsligt blir strandsatt i sin gamla hemstad ser han chansen att forfora Jamie en gång och for alla. Men det ar nu inte så latt att ta steget från att vara "bara vanner" till att bli "knullkompisar".

programme.title: Below Her Mouth
programme.desc: Dallas ar trott på sin tillvaro – hon sliter som taklaggare på dagen och traffar alskarinnor på natten – samma sak varje dag. Tills hon traffar den sjalvsakra och framgångsrika moderedaktoren Jasmine på en klubb.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Wingman, Inc
programme.desc: Bobby Tomkins jobbar som en professionell djurpsykolog och overtalats av sina vanner att praktisera sina fantastiska fardigheter som deras wingman bland tjejer. Och nar han antligen hittar sin egen efterlangtade karlek har han ingen aning om att Kristy ar hans absolut varsta tankbara rival. En ”man blocker” i varldsklass. Men i karlekens universum finns det inga spelregler, och enbart en av dem kan stå på tronen som nummer 1.

programme.title: My Best Friends Girl
programme.desc: Tank (Dane Cook) moter det ultimata vanskapsprovet nar hans basta van (Jason Biggs) ber honom att ta ut hans ex (Kate Hudson) på en usel dejt for att hon ska forstå vilken bra pojkvan han ar.

programme.title: Månadens anstalld (Employee of the Month)
programme.desc: Två extremt tavlingsinriktade Super Club-anstallda tavlar om titeln "Månadens anstalld", och om att vinna den snygga nya kassorskans hjarta i denna galna komedi.

programme.title: Min sommarprins
programme.desc: PR-krischefen Deidre och hennes assistent Mandy flyger in nar den upproriske prinsen Colin grips i småstaden Idaho. Men nar Deidre moter ett eget fiasko, får Mandy ovantade karriar- (och romantiska) mojligheter.

programme.title: Youth In Revolt
programme.desc: Michael Cera spelar rollen som Nick Twisp. En unik och alskvard tonåring med smak for livets sofistikerade gladjeamnen, såsom Sinatra och Fellini. På en campingsemester med familjen foralskar han sig i den vackra, intelligenta och frigjorda Sheeni Saunders (Portia Doubleday). Men geografi, familj och svartsjuka ex-partners konspirerar for att hålla Nick och Sheeni åtskilda. Efter uppmuntran från Sheeni overger Nick sitt tråkiga, forutsagbara liv och utvecklar ett rebelliskt alter ego: Francois Dillinger. Med mustasch, slips, djup rost och bad boy-attityd kan inget stoppa Francois från att vara tillsammans med Sheeni.

programme.title: The Last Kiss
programme.desc: Michael och Jenna ar ett par, och liksom alla andra 30-something-par står de infor en rad val i sitt forhållande. Men samtidigt som forpliktelserna blir allt fler, traffar Michael den unga skonheten Kim .

programme.title: Griffin and Phoenix
programme.desc: Nar Griffin har fått diagnosen att han har dodlig cancer bestammer han sig for att ta livet i egna hander och ha lite kul innan han dor. Samtidigt som tiden for hans liv rinner ut traffar han och blir kar i Phoenix - som också har en hemlighet.

programme.title: Cooking Up Love
programme.desc: Zoey hyr en matvagn och deltar i en reality-show på TV. Det går hett till mellan henne och den stilige grundaren till snabbmatskedjan, men nar Zoey får veta att han ar domare i tavlingen, blir det frasigt i pannan. Zoey ar fast besluten om att vinna rattvist och hon misstanker att "Mr-Too-Good-To-Be-True" ar ute efter hennes såsrecept och inte hennes hjarta.

programme.title: Modern Persuasion
programme.desc: En modern version av Jane Austens roman ”Övertalning”. Wren Cosgrove ar en lycklig och framgångsrik karriarkvinna som varje kvall kommer hem till sin katt. Nar hennes firma anlitas av Owen Jasper, han som var den ratte, så vacks gamla kanslor till liv och Wren får en ny chans att uppleva den sanna karleken.

programme.title: Just Friends
programme.desc: Får vi presentera Chris Bander. Highschool på nittiotalet var en pina: han var blyg, overviktig och hemligt foralskad i Jamie, hans enda kompis och tillika en av skolans mest populara hejarklacksledare. Men nar han antligen hade lyckats samla mod nog att gora en framstot, ville hon bara att de skulle vara vanner! I dag ar Chris en aslacker skivproducent i LA och kan valja bland en uppsjo av vackra och villiga tjejer. Och nar han plotsligt blir strandsatt i sin gamla hemstad ser han chansen att forfora Jamie en gång och for alla. Men det ar nu inte så latt att ta steget från att vara "bara vanner" till att bli "knullkompisar".

programme.title: Love Hurts
programme.desc: Pauls kvinnoaffarer ersatts med flera komiska incidenter nar han måste tillbringa en helg med sina foraldrar, sin fore detta fru och barnen.

programme.title: They Came Together
programme.desc: Nar Joel (Paul Rudd) och Molly (Amy Poehler) mottes var det hat vid forsta ogonkastet: hans storbolag Godiskompaniet hotade att stanga ner hennes bohemiska godisaffar. Plus att Joel fortfarande hade kanslor for sitt sexiga ex (Cobie Smulders). Men, trots allt så blir de kara, tills dess att de gor slut och Molly borjar dejta sin revisor (Ed Helms). Men, precis i sluttampen...tja, du får se helt enkelt. (Ledtråd: Joel håller ett stort tal och de hittar tillbaka till varandra.) Från regissoren som skapade Wet Hot American Summer, Wanderlust och Role Models kommer nu en helknapp och satirisk underminering av den romantiska komedigenren.

programme.title: Can You Keep a Secret
programme.desc: Emma sitter på ett plan som hon tror ar på vag att storta. Hon berattar darfor alla sina hemligheter for en snygg framling. Åtminstone tror hon att han ar en framling...tills hon traffar Jack, hennes foretags nya vd, som alltså vet varenda pinsam hemlighet om henne. Baserad på romanen med samma namn på New York Times bastsaljarlista, från forfattaren till ”En shopaholics bekannelser”, Sophie Kinsella.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Never Too Late
programme.desc: Fyra veteraner som overlevt Vietnamkrigets fånglager bestammer sig for att genomfora en sista flykt – från aldreboendet. Men att planera en rymning i ett senilt gang bjuder på utmaningar. Var och en bar på drommar, for vilka de ar beredda att satsa allt på detta sista hjaltedåd – om de bara kunde komma ihåg vad de skulle gora.

programme.title: I Love You Phillip Morris
programme.desc: Steve Russell (Jim Carrey) ar lyckligt gift med Debbie (Leslie Mann) och en monsterinvånare i staden dar de bor. En bilolycka får honom att drastiskt omvardera sitt liv. Steven inser genom en uppenbarelse att han ar gay och beslutar sig for att leva sitt liv fullt ut, aven om det innefattar att bryta mot lagen. Stevens nya syn på livet gor att han ganska snabbt hamnar i fangelset. Dar tar livet annu en ny vandning och han blir galet kar i Phillip Morris, en kanslosam och lågmald kille (Ewan McGregor). Stevens hangivelse att få leva ett liv i frihet tillsammans med Phillip driver Steve till fler och flera innovativa brott.

programme.title: Wingman, Inc
programme.desc: Bobby Tomkins jobbar som en professionell djurpsykolog och overtalats av sina vanner att praktisera sina fantastiska fardigheter som deras wingman bland tjejer. Och nar han antligen hittar sin egen efterlangtade karlek har han ingen aning om att Kristy ar hans absolut varsta tankbara rival. En ”man blocker” i varldsklass. Men i karlekens universum finns det inga spelregler, och enbart en av dem kan stå på tronen som nummer 1.

programme.title: Warm Bodies
programme.desc: Karleken overvinner allt... till och med den oemotståndliga lusten att ata din alskades hjarnmassa! I en inte så avlagsen framtid ar jorden befolkad av lika delarmanniskoatande zombier och zombiebekampande manniskor. Men nar den unge zombien R plotsligt får impulsen att radda den varmblodiga flickan Julie från ett zombieoverfall borjar en vanskap som kommer att vanda upp och ner på nyavarldsordningen! Forutsatt att Julie kan hållasig levande – och R kan hålla sig levande dodtillrackligt lange!

programme.title: Månadens anstalld (Employee of the Month)
programme.desc: Två extremt tavlingsinriktade Super Club-anstallda tavlar om titeln "Månadens anstalld", och om att vinna den snygga nya kassorskans hjarta i denna galna komedi.

programme.title: Jack and Jill Vs. The World
programme.desc: Den framgångsrike chefen Jack (Freddie Prinze Jr.) ar en metodisk och kontrollerad man som arbetar på en ny reklambyrå på Manhattan. Under en rokpaus på kontorets hustak moter Jack skådespelerskan Jill som just anlant till New York for att soka jobb. Hon berattar om sin situation så Jack ordnar ett jobb åt henne i en reklamkampanj som hans byrå ligger bakom. Nar han sedan lamnar Jill vid hennes hem upptacker han att hon bor i ett nedgånget lågbudgethotell, så Jack erbjudar då henne att bo i hans gastrum så lange. Detta visar sig få konsekvenser som ingen kunnat ana...

programme.title: We Too Together
programme.desc: Rob kampar med PTSD efter att ha kommit hem ifrån kriget. Långsamt lar han sig att overvinna sitt forflutna. Under julhelgerna moter han Gabriela som han fullstandigt faller for, och hon alskar honom precis som han ar. Vandning ar total och livet får åter en mening.

programme.title: The Last Kiss
programme.desc: Michael och Jenna ar ett par, och liksom alla andra 30-something-par står de infor en rad val i sitt forhållande. Men samtidigt som forpliktelserna blir allt fler, traffar Michael den unga skonheten Kim .

programme.title: Det nast basta (The Next Best Thing)
programme.desc: Yogainstruktoren Abbie och tradgårdsmastaren Robert delar det mesta i livet. Gladje. Sorg. Drommar. Och intresset for killar. Att Robert ar gay ar det enda som hindrar dem från att vara ett par. Sjalvklart festar de också tillsammans, så pass att de efter en helvild natt vaknar upp i varandras armar. De kan bara konstatera att det hant. Och att de gick for långt. På tok for långt. Beviset: ett positivt graviditetstest...

programme.title: No Stranger Than Love
programme.desc: Vad kan vara konstigare an att ett stort hål oppnar sig i Lucy Sherringtons vardagsrumsgolv? Jo, karleken, som det visar sig.Det finns inte en man i stan som inte ar kar i Lucy. Hon ar snall, sympatisk, rolig och lojal – hon ar den perfekta tjejen som inte kan gora något fel. Ändå har hon gått med på en traff med Clint som ar gift och coach for footballaget. Precis nar de ska påborja sin affar trillar Clint ner i ett hål som oppnar sig i Lucys vardagsrum. Men det ar inte vilket hål som helst; det ar det eviga morkrets interdimensionella och enkelriktade hål. Clint fastnar nere i hålet och svavar runt i ett oandlighetens mellantillstånd.

programme.title: They Came Together
programme.desc: Nar Joel (Paul Rudd) och Molly (Amy Poehler) mottes var det hat vid forsta ogonkastet: hans storbolag Godiskompaniet hotade att stanga ner hennes bohemiska godisaffar. Plus att Joel fortfarande hade kanslor for sitt sexiga ex (Cobie Smulders). Men, trots allt så blir de kara, tills dess att de gor slut och Molly borjar dejta sin revisor (Ed Helms). Men, precis i sluttampen...tja, du får se helt enkelt. (Ledtråd: Joel håller ett stort tal och de hittar tillbaka till varandra.) Från regissoren som skapade Wet Hot American Summer, Wanderlust och Role Models kommer nu en helknapp och satirisk underminering av den romantiska komedigenren.

programme.title: Hard Luck Love Song
programme.desc: Ett romantiskt drama kantat av countrymusik. Den charmerande men otursforfoljde Jesse driver runt utan riktning i livet. Nar en gammal flamma dyker upp inser Jesse att han står vid ett vagskal i livet och att han måste valja mellan att fortsatta fatta dåliga beslut eller att ta sig i kragen.

programme.title: Below Her Mouth
programme.desc: Dallas ar trott på sin tillvaro – hon sliter som taklaggare på dagen och traffar alskarinnor på natten – samma sak varje dag. Tills hon traffar den sjalvsakra och framgångsrika moderedaktoren Jasmine på en klubb.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E05 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 5, Latvia
programme.desc: This year Lauri Nami joins the starting list, back after last years injury in Romania

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E06 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 6, Serbia
programme.desc: The SCL train stopped in Zlatibor for the stage 6 of the MLO SCL. 11 compete for the title in the home country of legendary Ervin Katona.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E07 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 7, Bulgaria
programme.desc: Bulgaria hosts the next stage of the SCL. Current leader in the World Series is Matjaz Belsak, youngest competitor and strongest man of Slovenia.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E08 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 8, England
programme.desc: The competitors battle it out in the special event, the Atlas Steel Stone. This stone is made completely from iron and cannot be touched with any support.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E09 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 9, Finland
programme.desc: This stage sees the strongmen visit Vaasa, Finland. Residents here are familiar with the competition because some of the SCL icons are from their country.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E10 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 10, Finland - World championship under 105 kilograms
programme.desc: 38 athletes compete in the under 90kg and under 105kg SCL World Championships. From each weight class, the top 12 qualify for the finals.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E11 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 11, Romania Part 1
programme.desc: A two day, seven event battle with lots of spectators.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E12 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 12, Romania Part 2
programme.desc: Alex Moonen is leading. Part two of the competition in Romania showcases a new challenge - Hercules Hold.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E13 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 13, Curacao
programme.desc: In this stage in Curacao no one wants to lose the chance to fight for one kilo gold in World grand finals in Dubai.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E14 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 14, Portugal
programme.desc: The last chance to qualify for the World Grand Finale. Zageris and Belsak fight for the better position for the finals.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E15 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 15, Dubai World grand finals (Part 1)
programme.desc: We reach Dubai where we will crown the new champion for SCL 2016. This is part one of the world finals.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E16 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 16, Dubai World grand finals (Part 2)
programme.desc: In this last episode, the best athletes compete in Pole Push, Deadlift, Forward Hold and Loading.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E01 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 1, Norway
programme.desc: We are in beautiful Norway for the kick off of the 2017 MLO Strongman Champions League season. With partly cloudy weather and lots of snow, we have the perfect scenery for the athletes, who prepare for the first contest of the year.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E02 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 2, Germany
programme.desc: A definite highlight in this FIBO edition in Germany, Strongman Champions League introduced its new rules for a special team item. Graham Hicks tries here to set a New World Record on the biggest log in the world, currently held by Krzysztof Radzikowski. Boosted also by the presence of the acclaimed in the strongman circles names of Mark Felix and Danis Zageris.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E03 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 3, Lithuania
programme.desc: This weekend sees the Strongman Champions League Log Lift World Championships in Lithuania. Big lifting names such as Graham Hicks , Vidas Blekaitis and Vytatus Lalas are in the startlist to push some big numbers.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E04 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 4, Holland
programme.desc: The battle of the Dutch will take place this edition in Lichtenvoorde, a place very well known in Holland because of the famous “Black Cross”. The athletes will compete over six heavy events and the winner gets 25 Strongman Champions League ranking points.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E05 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 5, Serbia
programme.desc: Set in the beautiful mountain resort Zlatibor, the fifth stage of the Strongman Champions League 2017 sees 14 athletes from across the world competing for the gold medal of SCL Serbia 2017. The event welcomes top-athlete - and odds-on favourite - Matjaz Belsak (Slovenia), who has presented himself in an impressive shape so far. Can his opponents defeat him?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E06 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 6, Canada (Part 1)
programme.desc: The next two stages take place in Quebec. With eight events over two days, SCL Canada is a true ‘heavyweight’. The athletes compete in: Truck Pull, Deadlift with cars, Log Lift, and the Atlas Stones. The World’s Strongest Viking Jean-Francois Caron from Canada is a favourite, as well as current SCL leader Matjaz Belsak (Slovenia) and promising underdog Jimmy Paquet (Canada).

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E07 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 7, Canada (Part 2)
programme.desc: Welcome to the second day in Quebec. The athletes are fighting hard to win this two-day event. The last points of this SCL stage can be won over four outstanding disciplines: Power Stairs, Dumbbell Press, Keg Toss, and finally, the legendary Farmer’s Walk. Who will leave Canada with the yellow ‘Leader Shirt’?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E08 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 8, Finland (Part 1)
programme.desc: Stages 8 and 9 of the SCL are hosted in Vaasa, Finland, taking place over a spectacular two-day event. After 3 wins so far, Matjaz Belsak from Slovenia plans to extend his lead at the top of the table. Among the other 13 highly motivated strongmen, two SCL legends will make their comeback to the competition: Former World Champion of 2015, Krzysztof Radzikowski (Poland) and Dainis Zageris (Latvia).

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E09 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 9, Finland (Part 2)
programme.desc: The fight for the Finnish trophy continues. In this unmissable SCL event, the strongmen battle for the win in the Carry and Drag, the Forward Hold, Deadlifting with Cars and the Loading Race. Belsak, Radzikowski and Zageris look good after the first day, but the others haven’t given up yet.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E10 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 10, Finland Lightweight World Championship
programme.desc: This under 105kg category event is the ultimate preparation for up-and-coming strongman athletes before entering the heavy class. The Lightweight World Championship is a special every year in the SCL calendar as it sees new talents rise and many promising athletes who are gearing up for future tournaments. A total of 25 athletes from 16 different countries make their way to Kokkola, Finland

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E11 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 11, Romania
programme.desc: Situated in the very heart of the Carpathian Mountains, Sibiu is a Romanian town where the climate is pleasantly mild, offering some of the best weather conditions for a strongman event around Europe. All this, without doubt, set the mood for the high results and showtime vibes in Stage 11 of Strongman Champions League. The competition in Sibiu was organized in six different disciplines

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E12 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 12, Curacao
programme.desc: From now on every stage of these series will be more than crucial. Curacao is a beautiful Dutch island in the Caribbean, with a great atmosphere to hold another stage of the MLO Strongman Champions League. Let’s see who takes the title here and who will secure a place in the next stage.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E13 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 13, Jordan
programme.desc: Ten of the world’s strongest men gathered in Amman to compete in Jordan’s first-ever Truck-Pull Championship. The contestants race against the clock while pulling a 21-ton truck across the track. One of the most fierce competitors to take part in the event was four-time winner of the World’s Strongest Man competition, Brian Shaw.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E14 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 14, Greece
programme.desc: Taking place in Corinth, Greece, considered by many the cradle of the sports competition games, an epic strongman battle will mark the last stage before the upcoming big two-day season’s finale in Chetumal, Mexico. In front of more than 5000 spectators, the twelve athletes compete in Log Lifts, Card Deadlift, Conan’s Wheel and Loading.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E15 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 15, Mexico World Finals (Part 1)
programme.desc: The first day of the two-part finale sees the strongest men competing in Carry and Drag, Dumbbell Lift and the Truck Pull. Everything is possible in this heated fight for the crown against the backdrop of stunning Chetumal, Mexico.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E16 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 16, Mexico World Finals (Part 2)
programme.desc: On the second day of the grand finale of the 2017 Strongman Champions League, the athletes have a last chance to secure the medals in the spectacular four events Weight for Height, Deadlift Cars, Forward Hold and The Loading Medley. Be prepared for stunning performances – and even world records!

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E01 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 1, Norway - World Strongest Viking
programme.desc: Season 2018 begins with 14 strongest men in the world, all competing for the title. The competition kicks off in Norway. We’ll see typical Viking disciplines, team events and world records in heavy conditions in the land of snow and ice. They will suffer, they will freeze and fight in this first competition of the year for the title that they will carry on their shoulders throughout whole year.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E02 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 2, Germany - FIBO Power
programme.desc: The next stop in strongest league of the world is muscle capital, largest number of strong shoulders per capichampions league on the planet. It’s a FIBO - the biggest expo on planet Earth and the second stage of 2018 Strongman champions league, in Cologne, Germany.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E03 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 3, Abu Dhabi
programme.desc: For the first time in history, Strongman Champions League will set up competition in Abu Dhabi. The line-up of super athletes, who are part of the SCL, includes former world champions Dainis Zageris (Latvia) and Krzysztof Radzikowski (Poland), current world champion Matjaz Belsak (Slovenia) and biggest strongman in the World Sean O’Hagan (Ireland).

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E04 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 4, Holland (Part 1)
programme.desc: Strongman classic in land where there is no place for anything else excepts strength, fight and endurance. Here are fourteen of the strongest men, fighting for the title of strongest in Holland.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E05 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 5, Holland (Part 2)
programme.desc: We go back to Holland, where former champion Dainis Zageris is in leading position after the first three events. Alongside Radzikowski, he is in this moment favorite for world title, and also leader shirt holder.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E06 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 6, Finland
programme.desc: Stage six of Strongman champions league, 2018 is set back on north, in Finland. Here we have Matjaz Belsak, wearing SCL leader shirt, one of the biggest strongman in the World Mika Torro, fan favorite strongman in all over the World – Will Baggott, and also big name from Baltic – Aivars Smaukstelis

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E07 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 7, Serbia
programme.desc: Twelve strongman, including defending Worldchampion Matjaz Belsak from Slovenia , will compete on “Air spa” for the title of best in homeland country of Tesla, Pupin, Novak Djokovic. Matjaz Belsak is the SCL leader in this competition, chasing his third victory this season.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E08 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 8, Finland - U105 (Part 1)
programme.desc: The World championship in lightweights of the Strongman Champions League bring to us 50 strongmen from all over the world. All athletes are under 105 kilograms and for them this is the step up to the ultimate heavyweights.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E09 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 9, Finland - U105 (Part 2)
programme.desc: In this second stage of the World championship of lightweights we will find out who out of the 12 athletes will win the title in the under 105 kilogram category.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E10 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 10, Romania (Part 1)
programme.desc: The first part of SCL Romania 2018 will be hosted in Brasov. This episode features a new event for Strongman Champion League: “ The Chopper Pull”!

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E11 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 11, Romania (Part 2)
programme.desc: After three classical Strongman events – Dead lift, Loading and Front hold – and one historical, Chopper Pull for the first time in history of Strongman, now we go to find out who will take title in Romania. This is the second stage in Romania and it remains to be seen who will win the title; Aivars, Travis or Krzyzstof?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E12 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 12, Curacao (Part 1)
programme.desc: The next destination of Strongman Champions League is in a piece of paradise on earth – Curacao. We bring to you some special Strongman events like the Rock Lift, Tug of War and Weight for Height in this episode.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E13 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 13, Curacao (Part 2)
programme.desc: This is the last competition before the grand finals. After the first three events Zageris is in top place, but can O’Hagan, Baggott, Petursson and Ortmayer step into the final? Last chance some of them will find through events like Forward Hold, Truck Pull, Dead Lift and loading very big objects.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E14 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 14, Road to Mexico
programme.desc: We bring you 50 minutes of Strongman inside. Fears, inspiration, courage, the best and worst from our finalists and their expectation of the finals. We also go to Poland and Germany to represent one day in the training of Krzysztof Radzikowski and Dennis Kohlruss. See all the finalists for Mexico in their comfort zone here, with their backgrounds /motivations /family and friends.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E15 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 15, Mexico - World Finals (Part 1)
programme.desc: The first part of the Strongman Champions League 2018 finals in Mexico. The last twelve athletes all pushing their boundaries and testing their limits to take the World title.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E16 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 16, Mexico - World Finals (Part 2)
programme.desc: After 11 months and 14 competitions all over the world, it all comes down to the final in this episode. The strongmen must show their best skills and every mistake is expensive, so their concentration must be at the highest possible level. Will Krzysztof manage to take off back or will Dainis maintain his lead?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E01 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 1, World Strongest Viking
programme.desc: This year 14 athletes from all over the world came to Fefor to compete in 6 cruel events. Well see typical Viking disciplines on very heavy conditions in land of snow and ice, World records and athletes like the title defender Krzysztof Radzikowski, strongest guys from Holland and Germany and many more

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E02 SCL S6 Ep2 FIBO Power
programme.desc: The next stop in strongest league of the world is muscle capital, largest number of strong shoulders per capita in the World and of course, the most powerful host in Strongman champions league on the planet. It’s a FIBO - the biggest expo on planet Earth and the second stage of 2019 Strongman champions league, in Cologne, Germany.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E03 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 3, Turkey
programme.desc: On a spectacular beach in Alanya, the MLO Strongman Champions League Turkey was viewed by thousands of spectators over a two day battle. With 12 athletes at the start over 6 cruel events, like Marble Stone Lift, Truckpull and Deadlift cars. And with the comeback of Travis Ortmayer / USA, former stone king and world ranked competitor. Winner of several SCL stages in the past.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E04 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 4, Holland (Part 1)
programme.desc: Four times Strongest Man of Holland, Alex Moonen and the “Flying Dutchman” Kelvin de Ruiter competing here in Holland against 12 other strongest men in the world. There were 6 events in total, and 3 in this episode: The first event, a truckpull of 17.000 kg over 25 meters in max 75 seconds, was a real hard pull Also for the World Champion Truckpull, Holland’s runner-up Kelvin de Ruiter, but watch his amazing technique here.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E05 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 5, Holland (Part 2)
programme.desc: Strongest Man of Holland, Alex Moonen and the “Flying Dutchman” Kelvin de Ruiter, competing in Holland against 12 other strongest men in the world. There were 6 events in total, 3 in this second episode; a Viking-press of 150 kg with the current world record holder Luke Herrick. The fifth event, a front hold of 25 kg is loved or hated by the athletes and lastly, the Stones of Strength.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E06 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 6, Russia
programme.desc: An unbelievable TANK PULL of 50.000 kg was at the stage of SCL RUSSIA. Never seen this before! programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Downsizing can be a difficult transition and Jins objective is to make it as seamless as possible. Jins client is moving from a house in Port Credit to a luxurious condo close to the downtown core. They desire extra bedrooms for when their children are visiting, all the amenities, and waterfront views.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Mikes couple is looking for their luxurious dream home anywhere in between Toronto and Barrie near HWY 400 in a prestigious neighborhood. They have a large dog, tall family, and want to start a family of their own. This means they are going to need a lot of space and want the house to be fully renovated or brand-new. Mike is the perfect agent for this couple because he lives, eats, and breathes the luxury lifestyle.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: An amazing beachfront property is what Inezs couple is looking for and these top million dollar agents are sure to surpass their expectations. Inezs client currently lives in a condo and have one child, however, they desire a home that they can comfortably expand their family in.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Mikes friend invites him to an Indian wedding and tells him about his uncle who is looking for a luxury condo close to the airport. Daryl, Inez, and Jin support and donate to Mikes charity after winning a bet amongst them and the amount is determined by how long Mike lasts in the ring boxing against a professional. This client is looking for an investment property and a place for him to live when visiting.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E06 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Somewhere to spend the rest of their days surrounded by nature sounds like a paradise to retire in. Daryl and Jin play some golf to discuss a potential listing she has found and Mike aids Inez in purchasing a new vehicle. Daryls client has older children with their own families now so they are looking for a home with lots of land and nature. It is very important to them because they want to be able to have everyone comfortably visit and eventually retire here in a few years.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E08 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Moving in together can be stressful but fun because you are starting a new life together! Inezs client is selling their separate properties and looking for a house or condo in the city or beach area that is close to shopping, groceries, schools, etc. Inezs couple is not too picky and open to different kinds of properties. Daryl and Inez enjoy a beautiful bike ride along the beaches boardwalk to discuss her client and the perfect luxury listing he has found.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E09 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Agreeing on a vacation home is made much harder when these top million dollar agents have astounding listings. Mikes client is looking for a waterfront cottage with lots of land and privacy. What better way to check out some waterfront listings then from a helicopter? Debbie wants a family cottage that feels homey, however, Paul wants an impressive high-end cottage that he can bring his business clients to.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E10 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Remarrying is hard enough let alone combining two families under one roof. With a total of 4 children between the ages of 7 and 16 Jins client is definitely going to need lots of space and land in a safe neighborhood. Daryl, Inez, and Mike attend Jins band practice to support her and listen to the set list they have prepared for an upcoming charity event. Jin gets her nails done frequently and this time Daryl decides to join her for some much needed pampering.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E11 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Now that Kristen and Kane have opened an office in Toronto, they will be travelling a lot from Vancouver and want somewhere of their own to stay in. Daryl and the other top million dollar agents have a wide range to search over because Daryls client is willing to live an hour or two drive away from downtown Toronto. Daryl, Jin, and Mike meet up for lunch in Port Dover to discuss business and later in the episode Mike and Daryl get their hands dirty in the kitchen at Sababa Restaurant.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E13 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Deborah and Vezi are an international couple that want to live in Toronto for one year but has no idea where to start looking. Luckily for them Mike, Jin, Daryl, and Inez have teamed up to find them the home of their dreams. They agree to split the commission and throw a yacht party for the clients decision. Mike arranges a private plane for all four agents to go to Montreal and discuss in style what the client is looking for.

programme.desc: I ett desperat forsok att bli tagen på storre allvar reser ikonen Marilyn Monroe (Michelle Williams) till London 1956 for att spela mot legenden Laurence Olivier i “Prinsen och balettflickan”. Den omhetstorstande Marilyn kanner sig overgiven av maken Arthur Miller och attraherad av Oliviers assistent, den unge Colin Clark. Colin blir snart Marilyns fasta och trygga punkt, samtidigt som han också blir Oliviers endahopp att kunna slutfora sin film genom sin formåga att hålla den impulsiva Marilyn i schakt. Upp over oronen foralskadar det nu Colins hjarta som riskerar att krossas av varldens storsta och vackraste filmstjarna!

programme.title: The Fifth Estate
programme.desc: De borjade med att skapa en undergroundwebbplats och kom att bli varldens mest efterlysta personer. Men nar WikiLeaksgrundarnaJulian Assange och Daniel Domscheit-Berg kom over den storsta mangden sekretessbelagd underrattelseinformation som någonsin har lackt ut från det amerikanska forsvarsministeriet borjade en intern kamp. For vad ar priset for den fria varldens storsta hemligheter? Och vad kommer det att kosta att avsloja dem?

programme.title: Hercules I New York
programme.desc: Forvisad från Mount Olympus skickas Hercules, (Arnold Schwarzenegger), till jorden dar han hittar sann karlek och borjar en lovande karriar som kroppsbyggare.

programme.title: A Late Quartet
programme.desc: Nar den alskade cellisten i en varldsberomd stråkkvartett får Parkinsons sjukdom hanger gruppens framtid plotsligt på en skor tråd. Undertryckta kanslor, starka egon och passioner hotar deras vanskap och samarbete. Nar de ska spela jubileumskonserten for att fira sin 25:e sasong, kanske deras sista, kan bara deras starka band och kraften i musiken bevara deras arv. Inspirerad av Beethovens Opus 131 i C-moll hyllar A LATE QUARTET kammarmusiken och det kulturella New York.

programme.title: Daredevil
programme.desc: Mot DAREDEVIL - Marvels legendariske superhjalte, kand som Mannen utan fruktan. Med spektakulara specialeffekter, slagsmålsscener utver det vanliga och nonstop action. På dagtid arbetar den blinde Matt Murdock som advokat, på natten ar han DAREDEVIL. En maskerad hjalte som bevakar stadens morka grander.

programme.title: A Little Bit Of Heaven
programme.desc: Kate Hudson ar perfekt i rollen som den sprudlande vackra Marley, en ung karriarkvinna som plotsligt drabbas av cancer. Marley ar en riktig flirt,som aldrig har varit kar, men nar lakaren, spelad av oemotståndlig Gael García Bernal, kunde karlek kanske andå vara den basta medicinen?

programme.title: Promised Land
programme.desc: Det har dramat foljer två skolkamrater, Hancock och Danny, efter examen. Hancock och hans flickvan som ar en cheerleader ger sig ivag till medelklassens tillhåll utom rackhåll for Danny och hans psykotiska fru Bev.

programme.title: In Time
programme.desc: I en framtid dar tid ar bokstavligen pengar och åldrande stannar vid 25 år, ar det enda sattet att hålla sig vid liv att tjana, stjala eller arva mer tid. Kommer Salas att leva minut till minut, tills en tidsfall ger honom tillgång till den rika varlden, dar han lagar sig med en vacker ung arvtagare for att forstora det korrupta systemet.

programme.title: Man on Fire
programme.desc: MAN ON FIRE ar en gripande thriller med Oscar® belonade Denzel Washington i huvudrollen. Han spelar Creasy, en f.d. utbrand CIA agent som tappat livsgnistan. Creasy overtalas av sin van Rayburn (Christopher Walken) att skydda en tioårig flicka i Mexico City dar barnkidnappningar tillhor vardagen. Creasy kommer flickan nara och deras relation gor att han återfår viljan att leva. Nar hon sedan blir kidnappad tappar Creasy allt forstånd. Han ger sig ut på en vansinnesjakt for att finna henne och ingenting kan stoppa honom.

programme.title: A Bronx Tale
programme.desc: 9-årige Calogero bor i ett italienskt kvarter i Bronx. En dag bevittnar han ett mord som begås av den lokale maffiabossen Sonny. Calogero valjer att inte tjalla på Sonny, och som tack blir Sonny hans extrapappa. Calogeros hederlige far kan dock inte acceptera att sonen fostras till en gangster.

programme.title: A Time to Kill
programme.desc: Filmatiseringen av John Grishams bastsaljare Juryn - A Time to Kill aren stark och gripande historia regisserad av Joel Schumacher (Batman Forever, Klienten). Sandra Bullock, Samuel L. Jackson, Matthew McConaughey och Kevin Spacey spelar huvudrollerna i denna film om ett mordfall som blåser liv i rasmotsattningarna i en liten stad i Mississippi. Mitt i kaoset av marscherande aktivister, Ku Klux Klan-terror, mediahysteri och brutala upplopp forsoker en orutinerad men idealistisk ung advokat gora sig hord i sin kamp for rattvisa.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Cypher
programme.desc: I ett skuggigt rike av foretagsspionage, snubblar en uttråkad alla in i ett nat av bedrageri och blir en omedveten spion. Nar han navigerar i forraderi och svek, samarbetar han med en forforisk gåta for att avsloja chockerande sanningar och återta sin identitet.

programme.title: Shes The Man
programme.desc: Nar Violas bror drar till London passar hon på att hanga på hans internatskola. Utkladd till sin bror blir Viola kar i en av fotbollsspelarna i skollaget men inser snart att det ar betydligt fl er an hon (han) som har karleksproblem… Duke vill ha Olivia som gillar Sebastian som egentligen ar Viola. Violas brorsa traffar Monique så hon hatar Olivia som hanger med Duke for att gora Sebastian svartsjuk. Sebastian ar ju egentligen Viola som ar kar i Duke som tror att hon ar en snubbe... Hangde ni med?

programme.title: The Girl Next Door
programme.desc: Matthew Kidman (Emile Hirsch), en vanlig kille som går sista året på gymnasiet, blir kar i den nyinflyttade grannen Danielle (Elisha Cuthbert från TV-serien “24”), en sexig och snygg tjej som tycks ha allt. Snart får han veta att hon ar en mycket speciell tjej - Danielle har ett forflutet som fore detta porrstjarna. Matthew riskerar allt och får uppleva saker aldrig kunnat forestalla sig...

programme.title: Tillbaka till Yorkshire
programme.desc: Arthur Morrison får reda på att han har cancer och att han bara har några veckor kvar att leva. Hans vuxna son Blake reser till Yorkshire for att bo hos sin mamma i byn dar han vaxte upp. Nar Arthurs tillstånd forvarras ser Blake tillbaka på sitt forhållande med pappan. Han minns saker de gjort tillsammans, fortroligheten mellan dem och aven de forbistringar de haft. Nar fadern dor borjar Morrison fundera kring det band de haft. Han ger tydligt uttryck for motsattningar, frustration, karlek och forlust som alla ar delar i det komplicerade forhållande som finns mellan en far och hans son.

programme.title: What We Did On Our Holiday
programme.desc: Doug (David Tennant) och Abi (Rosamund Pike) ar två helt vanliga foraldrar med tre charmiga men valdigt excentriska barn. Nar det hårda foraldralivet hotar deras mentala halsa och aktenskap så bestammer de sig for att ta med barnen på en resa till Skottland till ett stort slaktkalas och for att halsa på Dougs minst sagt knappa pappa Gordie (Billy Connolly). Det som skulle bli en forsoningsresa forvandlas snabbt till ett hysteriskt roligt socialt katastrofområde nar osamja,
